<F P=100> India </F>
<H3> <TI>   Pakistan Reportedly To Close Consulate in Bombay </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  BK2003124594 Delhi All India Radio Network in English 1230 
GMT 20 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK2003124594 </F>
<F P=104>  Delhi All India Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Pakistan has decided to close down its Consulate 
General office in Bombay with immediate effect. The Indian high 
commissioner in Islamabad has been called by the Foreign 
Ministry and informed of its decision. 

</TEXT>

