Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The Council of Jewish Settlements in Judaea, 
Samaria, and the Gaza Strip [CJSJSG] has decided to oppose the 
evacuation of Jews from Hebron by any means. 
  At a special meeting in Qiryat Arba', the council made 
