GMT 23 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2303102994 </F>
<F P=104>  Algiers Radio Algiers Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Security services announced that two Frenchmen were 
assassinated yesterday around 2230 in Birkhadem in the capital's 
suburbs. The same sources said that Michel Drouaier, a partner 
in a private enterprise in Algeria, and his 24-year-old son, 
Pascal Valery, were killed by cold steel weapons by five 
terrorists inside their home in Charbonier district in 
Birkhadem. 

