<H3> <TI>   'Arafat, Russian Envoy, Discuss Hebron Resolution </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD2203180594 Algiers Voice of Palestine in Arabic 1702 GMT 
22 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2203180594 </F>
<F P=104>  Algiers Voice of Palestine </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Brother President Abu-'Ammar [Yasir 'Arafat] this 
morning met with Viktor Posuvalyuk, the special envoy of Russian 
President Yeltsin, for the fourth time in two days. At the 
meeting, they examined the latest developments and contacts on 
the implementation of the [UN] Security Council Resolution 904 
on the massacre at the al-Ibrahimi Mosque in Hebron, as well as 
the forthcoming meeting of the volunteers [as heard] due to take 
place in Cairo on 24 March on [Palestinian] security. 

</TEXT>

