<H3> <TI>   Ettajdid Party Member Arrested for Criticizing Elections </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD2203135594 Paris Radio France International in French 1230 
GMT 22 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2203135594 </F>
<F P=104>  Paris Radio France International </F>


