<H3> <TI>   Peres Comments on Hebron Residents' Security </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  TA2303115594 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 1100 GMT 23 
Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA2303115594 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Hebrew </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Foreign Minister Shim'on Peres said that the 
government would publicly announce its decision when it decided 
whether or not to evacuate the Jews from Hebron. The government 
does not just have intentions, it also reaches decisions, Peres 
said. The foreign minister added that there is only one address 
for the security of all Hebron residents, both Arabs and Jews, 
and that is the Israeli Government. Minister Peres was speaking 
at a political debate in the Knesset. 

</TEXT>

