<F P=102> JN2303092394 Manama WAKH in Arabic 0800 GMT 23 Mar 94 </F>
<F P=103> JN2303092394 </F>
<F P=104>  Manama WAKH </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Salalah, 23 Mar (WAKH)--King Husayn of Jordan left 
Salalah today at the end of a private three-day visit to the 
Sultanate of Oman. 
  The Jordanian monarch held several meetings with His Majesty 
Sultan Qabus Bin-Sa'id in which bilateral relations and means to 
bolster them were reviewed, in addition to current developments 
in the Arab and international arenas and issues of mutual 
concern. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

