<H3> <TI>   Jordanian King Husayn Arrives on Visit </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  JN2303113794 Manama WAKH in Arabic 1110 GMT 23 Mar 94 </F>
<F P=103> JN2303113794 </F>
<F P=104>  Manama WAKH </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Arabic </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Doha, 23 Mar (WAKH)--King Husayn of Jordan arrived 
in Doha from Muscat this morning on a two-day visit to the State 
of Qatar. 
  His Highness Shaykh Khalifah Bin-Hamad Al Thani, amir of the 
State of Qatar, led those who received the Jordanian monarch. 
He was also received by His Highness Shaykh Hamad Bin-Khalifah 
Al Thani, heir apparent and defense minister, ministers, and 
ranking officials. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

